> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Shutdown Sequence Change**: To fix the `RequestWrap` crash, the `camera_.release()` call will now happen *before* `camera_thread_.join()`. This is necessary to unblock the GStreamer pipeline and prevent race conditions within `libcamerasrc`.

